---

## Lessons
Total length: 2 Weeks

(list each lesson with main topic(s))
The lessons are doubled.
The anatomy of a web page and HTML structure
Intro to Javascript: basic functions, basic events, and variables 
Elements as objects and relationship between HTML and JavaScript
Conditional statements and basic strings 
SQA (Software Quality Analysis) 

---

## Assessments
(list summative and/or formative assessments used)
End of unit PROJECT
Project testing and peer feedback 
